srtrelay (1.4.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * fix srt-listener getting stuck with multiple clients re-/disconnecting
  * ignore SRT streamid keys sent by Blackmagic Atem Mini Pro
  * disconnect client early if stream is not found/is duplicated, thanks to @hanatyan128

